<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-6">Installation</h1>

<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
  Get botster running on your machine.
</p>

<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mt-8 mb-3">Requirements</h2>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-400 space-y-1 mb-6">
  <li>macOS or Linux</li>
  <li>Git</li>
  <li>A GitHub account</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mt-8 mb-3">Install</h2>
<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
  Download the latest release and add it to your PATH:
</p>
<pre class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-sm text-zinc-300 font-mono overflow-x-auto mb-6"><code># macOS
curl -fsSL https://trybotster.com/install.sh | sh</code></pre>

<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mt-8 mb-3">Verify</h2>
<pre class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-sm text-zinc-300 font-mono overflow-x-auto"><code>botster --version</code></pre>
